    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "County Superintendent Watkins\nstated today that the attendance Of\nthe schools throughout the county is\nthe best in years. The attendance for\nthe first three months of the new\nterm shows decided increase over\nlast year. Mr.. Watkins says the fine\nweather has a great deal to do with\nthe pupils attending school."
    }
